normally. in a case like this.
we would go after your accuser.

1014
00:49:11.315 --> 00:49:13.807
- What's her name? Emily.
- Eden.

1015
00:49:15.219 --> 00:49:17.419
I mean. with a name like
that. no wonder she fucked you.

1016
00:49:19.690 --> 00:49:21.056
Standard procedure

1017
00:49:21.725 --> 00:49:24.024
