of sexual promiscuity.

1019
00:49:26.997 --> 00:49:29.193
Better yet. mental illness.

1020
00:49:29.567 --> 00:49:31.798
Then we may have
a fighting chance.

1021
00:49:31.869 --> 00:49:35.931
Did she ever mention anything
about sleeping with other clients?

1022
00:49:36.006 --> 00:49:37.872
What? No.

1023
00:49:38.175 --> 00:49:39.871
Oh. I'll have a...

1024
