social media accounts.

1025
00:49:42.780 --> 00:49:43.907
Maybe we'll find something.

1026
00:49:43.981 --> 00:49:47.042
Worst comes to worst. we'll
hire a private investigator.

1027
00:49:47.485 --> 00:49:48.748
Well. how's that gonna help?

1028
00:49:48.819 --> 00:49:51.653
Well. if we can
discredit Miss Eden.

1029
00:49:51.722 --> 00:49:56.490
we may be able to threaten <i>Vanity
Fair</i> with a character defamation lawsuit.

1030
00:49:56.560 --> 00:49:59.655
Though just because she fucked around
doesn't mean she wanted to fuck you.

1031
00:49:59.730 --> 00:50:02.175
- I didn't fuck her. Jon.
- And. honestly. in this day and age.

1032
00:50:02.199 --> 00:50:05.465
