ourselves and go publish it anyway.

1033
00:50:05.870 --> 00:50:06.894
[sighs]

1034
00:50:07.171 --> 00:50:08.171
Shit.

1035
00:50:09.874 --> 00:50:13.038
Now that I'm thinking about
it. the smarter play here...

1036
00:50:15.112 --> 00:50:16.774
We got to get to the girl.

1037
00:50:17.515 --> 00:50:19.143
Convince her to retract.

1038
00:50:21.285 --> 00:50:22.514
What do you know about her?

1039
00:50:23.187 --> 00:50:24.780
Does she need money?
Can she be bought?

1040
00:50:25.422 --> 00:50:27.516
- What does she have to lose?
- I don't know.

1041
00:50:27.591 --> 00:50:29.302
I don't understand why
she's doing this to me.

1042
00:50:29.326 --> 00:50:30.453
I really don't.

1043
00:50:31.862 --> 00:50:34.195
We got along great.
We were friends.

1044
00:50:38.202 --> 00:50:40.002
[sighs] Maybe if I could
just reach out to her

1045
00:50:40.070 --> 00:50:41.470
and ask her what she wants...

1046
00:50:41.539 --> 00:50:43.906
Whoa. whoa. whoa. No.
for Christ's sake. Noah.

1047
00:50:43.974 --> 00:50:46.375
under no circumstances
are you to contact this woman.

1048
00:50:46.510 --> 00:50:48.035
But nothing happened between us.

1049
00:50:48.245 --> 00:50:50.305
I don't care if you fucked
her. if she fucked you.

1050
00:50:50.381 --> 00:50:53.146
if you shoved carrots up each
other's asses and ate them.

1051
00:50:53.217 --> 00:50:54.810
do not reach out to this woman.

1052
00:50:54.985 --> 00:50:57.585
Jon. I went to prison for three
years for a crime I didn't commit.

1053
00:50:57.621 --> 00:50:58.554
Eh. don't remind me.

1054
00:50:58.622 --> 00:51:00.591
It was the nadir of my
professional career.

1055
00:51:00.658 --> 00:51:02.092
I know I'm not guilty here.

1056
00:51:02.159 --> 00:51:04.321
How can it be possible
there's nothing else I can do?

1057
00:51:04.395 --> 00:51:07.297
I'm sorry. Solloway. it's like the
French Revolution out there right now.

1058
00:51:07.364 --> 00:51:10.425
The best I can offer is we
hire a private investigator.

1059
00:51:10.501 --> 00:51:12.436
we see if she's
retained a lawyer.

1060
00:51:12.503 --> 00:51:16.372
and we float some under-the-table
settlement for her silence.

1061
00:51:16.574 --> 00:51:20.204
I don't have the money to pay for a
private investigator. Or Eden. Or you.

1062
00:51:21.345 --> 00:51:23.143
I'm putting my daughter's
wedding on credit.

1063
00:51:25.249 --> 00:51:27.049
Been banking on this
book and this movie to...

1064
00:51:27.985 --> 00:51:29.419
put me back in the black.

1065
00:51:33.591 --> 00:51:36.527
I should call my crisis
PR girl right away.

1066
00:51:36.961 --> 00:51:40.159
She's the best. Anthony
Weiner. Eliot Spitzer. Weinstein.

1067
00:51:40.230 --> 00:51:41.230
But she fired him.

1068
00:51:43.400 --> 00:51:44.925
Oh. God. [exhales]

1069
00:51:45.002 --> 00:51:46.002
All right.

1070
00:51:47.071 --> 00:51:49.199
I'll set up a call for
all of us tomorrow.

1071
00:51:49.740 --> 00:51:52.300
We'll discuss next steps
in case the worst happens.

1072
00:51:52.376 --> 00:51:53.867
In the meantime. go home.

1073
00:51:53.944 --> 00:51:55.640
Cancel all public appearances.

1074
00:51:55.713 --> 00:51:59.309
And. for crying out loud.
keep your hands to yourself.

1075
00:51:59.683 --> 00:52:01.208
And circle your wagons.

1076
00:52:02.286 --> 00:52:03.286
Meaning what?

1077
00:52:05.255 --> 00:52:06.416
Tell your family.

1078
00:52:12.062 --> 00:52:13.325
[sigh]

1079
