[woman over P.A.] <i>Flight 11 7 to Tel
Aviv will now be departing from Gate 45.</i>

1080
00:52:20.604 --> 00:52:24.302
<i>Flight 11 7 to Tel Aviv will
now be departing from Gate 45.</i>

1081
00:52:31.548 --> 00:52:33.073
