1102
00:54:29.733 --> 00:54:31.759
Eden. I just want
to talk to you.

1103
00:54:31.835 --> 00:54:33.565
Noah. I'm a publicist.

1104
00:54:33.637 --> 00:54:35.877
and I'm gonna give you some
