1122
00:55:18.916 --> 00:55:20.942
Oh. my God. At least
be honest with yourself.

1123
00:55:21.018 --> 00:55:23.351
No. you be honest with
yourself. You remember...

1124
00:55:23.420 --> 00:55:24.898
you remember how you
were dressed that night?

1125
00:55:24.922 --> 00:55:26.466
