to get back to my job.

1128
00:55:30.861 --> 00:55:32.022
No. Eden.

1129
00:55:34.498 --> 00:55:37.468
You wanted to fuck
me. and I walked away.

1130
00:55:37.768 --> 00:55:39.245
Now. I don't know
if that pissed you off.

1131
00:55:39.269 --> 00:55:42.068
and this is some kind of sick
revenge. But I have a family.

1132
00:55:42.139 --> 00:55:43.573
I have two daughters.

1133
00:55:44.374 --> 00:55:47.538
And you're gonna ruin my life.
So. please. this is not a game.

1134
00:55:53.617 --> 00:55:55.552
I'm not afraid of
you anymore. Noah.

1135
00:55:56.186 --> 00:55:57.381
Afraid of me?

1136
00:55:58.355 --> 00:56:00.221
I didn't go looking
