1137
00:56:00.891 --> 00:56:02.416
A reporter called me. and...

1138
00:56:02.826 --> 00:56:04.522
I decided to tell the truth.

1139
00:56:05.062 --> 00:56:06.792
She called you? Why?

1140
00:56:07.130 --> 00:56:08.962
Noah. I'm doing you a favor.

1141
00:56:09.633 --> 00:56:13.263
I won't tell anybody you stalked
me here. but you need to leave now.

1142
00:56:13.604 --> 00:56:16.369
Or everyone's gonna
know about this.

1143
00:56:18.809 --> 00:56:21.108
[indistinct chatter]

1144
00:56:21.311 --> 00:56:22.311
Seriously.

1145
00:56:24.514 --> 00:56:27.109
