Perfect timing. We were just
about to sing "Happy Birthday."

1160
00:57:15.365 --> 00:57:17.459
[chuckles] Great.

1161
00:57:17.668 --> 00:57:19.102
- Hey. Dad.
- Hey. Trev.

1162
00:57:19.903 --> 00:57:22.338
- Nice cake.
- Thank you.

1163
00:57:24.975 --> 00:57:28.309
Lasagna for my
birthday. Thank you.

1164
00:57:30.113 --> 00:57:31.206
How's Whitney?

1165
00:57:31.448 --> 00:57:33.314
Uh. she's good.
She's-she's great.

1166
00:57:33.383 --> 00:57:35.113
