1172
00:57:49.132 --> 00:57:51.612
Uh. do you want some? The
kids and I are about to have a toast.

1173
00:57:51.969 --> 00:57:54.200
- What. even Stacey?
- She can have a little.

1174
00:57:54.271 --> 00:57:55.500
- [phone ringing]
- Sure.

1175
00:57:59.943 --> 00:58:01.321
That's so weird. This
New York number

1176
00:58:01.345 --> 00:58:03.723
