and they won't leave a voice mail.

1177
00:58:03.747 --> 00:58:04.747
Hello.

1178
00:58:05.749 --> 00:58:07.809
Yeah. this is Helen Solloway.

1179
00:58:08.585 --> 00:58:10.281
I'm sorry. from what magazine?

1180
00:58:11.655 --> 00:58:13.248
[quietly] <i>Vanity Fair.</i>

1181
00:58:14.124 --> 00:58:16.252
- Helen...
- Uh. okay. I need two minutes.

1182
00:58:16.626 --> 00:58:17.937
Can we start
drinking without you?

1183
00:58:17.961 --> 00:58:19.395
[whispers] It's
just two minutes.

1184
00:58:19.997 --> 00:58:22.694
- Helen...
- Okay. Petra. what can I do for you?

1185
00:58:25.002 --> 00:58:29.098
[Stacey huffing and puffing]

1186
00:58:37.447 --> 00:58:39.382
[instrumental music playing]

